<html lang="sk">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<title>Contract</title>
		<style>
			@keyframes fadeIn {
				from {
					opacity: 0;
				}
				to {
					opacity: 1;
				}
			}

			@keyframes slideInUp {
				from {
					opacity: 0;
					transform: translateY(20px);
				}
				to {
					opacity: 1;
					transform: translateY(0);
				}
			}

			body {
				font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				min-height: 100vh;
				background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #f0fdf4 0%, #f8fafc 55%, #ecfdf5 100%);
				color: #111827;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
			}

			.page {
				width: min(94vw, 720px);
				padding: 32px;
				background: #f9fef7;
				border: 1px solid #d1f3d4;
				border-radius: 24px;
				box-shadow: 0 24px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
				animation: slideInUp 0.8s ease-out;
			}

			h1 {
				margin-top: 0;
				color: #166534;
				border-bottom: 3px solid #86efac;
				padding-bottom: 12px;
				animation: slideInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.1s both;
			}

			h2 {
				color: #15803d;
				border-left: 4px solid #86efac;
				padding-left: 12px;
				animation: slideInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
			}

			p {
				line-height: 1.75;
				color: #334155;
				animation: slideInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.3s both;
			}

			ul {
				color: #475569;
				animation: slideInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s both;
			}

			a {
				color: #059669;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			a:hover {
				color: #047857;
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="page">
			<h1>Contract & Services</h1>
			<p>This page contains general contract information and a quick overview of terms.</p>
			
			<h2>Service Overview</h2>
			<p>I offer comprehensive web development and consulting services tailored to your needs. Whether you need a new website, optimization, or custom solutions, I'm here to help.</p>
			
			<h2>Scope of Work</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Website Development</strong> - Custom static and dynamic sites</li>
				<li><strong>Web Design</strong> - Responsive, modern layouts</li>
				<li><strong>Performance Optimization</strong> - Speed and efficiency improvements</li>
				<li><strong>Technical Consulting</strong> - Architecture and best practices</li>
				<li><strong>Maintenance & Support</strong> - Ongoing updates and fixes</li>
			</ul>
			
			<h2>General Terms</h2>
			<p>Work is completed on a project basis. Payment terms are net 30 days. All deliverables include source code documentation and support for deployment.</p>
			
			<h2>Timeline & Communication</h2>
			<p>I maintain regular communication throughout projects and provide updates on progress. Typical project timelines range from 2-6 weeks depending on scope and complexity.</p>
			
			<h2>Rates & Pricing</h2>
			<p>Project pricing is customized based on requirements. I offer competitive rates and can work within various budget constraints. Contact for a detailed quote.</p>
			
			<h2>Questions?</h2>
			<p>For more information or to discuss your project, reach out via GitHub or email. I'm happy to discuss your vision and provide recommendations.</p>
			
			<hr style="margin: 2rem 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #dbeafe;">
			<p><a href="/index">← Back to Welcome</a></p>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
